TEST;25-MAR-1987 07:18:24.59;YEN MAY RISE TO 140 TO THE DLR, NIKKEIREN SAYS;  The yen could rise to 140 yen to the dollar, a leading Japanese businessman said.     Bumpei Otsuki, president of the influential Japan Federation of Employers' Associations, (Nikkeiren), told reporters: The yen might rise as far as 140 (to the dollar). The U.S. Economy is not good

